<p style="margin-bottom:6pt; padding:0in 5.4pt">$56,711.58</p>
</td>
<td style="width:116.9pt; border-style:none solid solid none; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-bottom-color:windowtext; border-right-width:1pt; border-right-color:windowtext" width="156">
<p style="margin-bottom:6pt; padding:0in 5.4pt">&ldquo;uses multimedia storytelling to help spread the powerful stories of positive and inspiring programs, individuals, and events&rdquo;</p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td style="width:116.85pt; border-right-width:1pt; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-left-width:1pt; border-style:none solid solid; border-right-color:windowtext; border-bottom-color:windowtext; border-left-color:windowtext" width="156">
