<p style="margin-bottom:6pt; padding:0in 5.4pt">University of North Carolina-Chapel Hill</p>
</td>
<td style="width:116.85pt; border-style:none solid solid none; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-bottom-color:windowtext; border-right-width:1pt; border-right-color:windowtext" width="156">
<p style="margin-bottom:6pt; padding:0in 5.4pt">Marketing Communications Manager, Innovate Carolina</p>
</td>
