<p style="margin-bottom:6pt; padding:0in 5.4pt">Fully report all public service expenditures under one category.</p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td style="width:155.8pt; border-right-width:1pt; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-left-width:1pt; border-style:none solid solid; border-right-color:windowtext; border-bottom-color:windowtext; border-left-color:windowtext" width="208">
<p style="margin-bottom:6pt; padding:0in 5.4pt">Academic Support</p>
</td>
<td style="width:155.85pt; border-style:none solid solid none; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-bottom-color:windowtext; border-right-width:1pt; border-right-color:windowtext" width="208">
<p style="margin-bottom:6pt; margin-left:0.5in; padding:0in 5.4pt">- Report expenses for academic support into 3 sub-categories: Instruction, Research, and Public Service</p>
</td>
<td style="width:155.85pt; border-style:none solid solid none; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-bottom-color:windowtext; border-right-width:1pt; border-right-color:windowtext" width="208">
<p style="margin-bottom:6pt; padding:0in 5.4pt">Improve transparency of academic support expenditures.</p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td style="width:155.8pt; border-right-width:1pt; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-left-width:1pt; border-style:none solid solid; border-right-color:windowtext; border-bottom-color:windowtext; border-left-color:windowtext" width="208">
<p style="margin-bottom:6pt; padding:0in 5.4pt">Institutional Support</p>
</td>
