<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><span lang="IT" style="background:white"><a href="#_ftnref392" name="_ftn392" title=""><span contenteditable="false" tabindex="-1"><sup data-widget="footnotemarker">392</sup></span></a> </span>&ldquo;The Innovative and Entrepreneurial University: Higher Education, Innovation &amp; Entrepreneurship in Focus,&rdquo; U.S. Department of Commerce, October 2013,&nbsp;<a href="https://www.eda.gov/pdf/The_Innovative_and_Entrepreneurial_University_Report.pdf">https://www.eda.gov/pdf/The_Innovative_and_Entrepreneurial_University_Report.pdf</a>.</p>
